# Architecture Overview (v2)

Monorepo: React/Vite at root, Express/PostgreSQL in `backend/`, Electron in `electron/`, shared packages in `shared/`.

## Layer Stack

```
Electron â†’ React â†’ apiClient (/api/v1) or SQLite IPC â†’ Express â†’ modules (routesâ†’servicesâ†’repositories) â†’ FinancialPostingService â†’ PostgreSQL
```

Shared calculation logic: `shared/financial-core/`, `shared/report-engines/`.

## Runtime Modes

| Mode | Trigger | Data path |
|------|---------|-----------|
| Offline SQLite | `VITE_LOCAL_ONLY=true` | Electron â†’ sqliteBridge â†’ services/database/ |
| LAN/API client | `VITE_LOCAL_ONLY=false` | apiClient â†’ /api/v1 :3000/:3001 â†’ PostgreSQL |
| API server | backend/dist/index.js | PostgreSQL + migrations on startup |

## Strangler: New Code Uses v2

Legacy `backend/src/routes/` + flat `services/` still exist as delegates. **New features** go in `backend/src/modules/<domain>/` with `TenantRepository` subclasses.

## Where to Put New Code

| Concern | Location |
|---------|----------|
| Domain API | `backend/src/modules/<domain>/` (routes, services, repositories) |
| GL writes | `FinancialPostingService` only |
| Migrations | `database/migrations/NNN_name.sql` |
| Financial/report logic | `shared/financial-core/`, `shared/report-engines/` |
| API client | `services/api/` (base `/api/v1`) |
| UI | `components/<domain>/` or `modules/<feature>/` |

## Reference Features

- Dashboard snapshots: `modules/dashboard/` â†’ `GET /dashboard/snapshots`
- Financial posting: `FinancialPostingService` â†’ `JournalRepository`
- Custom reports: `modules/reporting/`

## Anti-Patterns

- SQL in routes; direct GL writes outside FinancialPostingService
- Missing tenant_id; editing AUTO-GENERATED backend/financial files
- New calculation logic in components/ (use shared/report-engines/)
- Broad useAppContext() in new code

